{"tid":1711104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[無可疑] 墳場夫妻墮樓亡　警方指二人「拜祭父母後自殺」","createTime":"2019-11-12T10:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T09:31:46.000Z","uid":226548,"like":4,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ea9ca378acd06ee5d137210e7bdbefdfb61e0a51","tid":1711104,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://clo01.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/12116-02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fclo01.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F12116-02.png&h=5097a39e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  柴灣發生夫妻墮樓命案，今日(12日)下午1時19分，一對年約50歲男女，被途人發現在歌連臣角墳場第六座靈灰安置所(追遠堂)對開地下昏迷，於是報警求助，救護員到場將兩人送院搶救，惜最終不治，死者親友接報到醫院了解。<br />\n<br />\n  警方接報到場調查，在追遠堂6樓圍欄邊，發現一個反轉的垃圾桶及檢獲遺書，相信兩人踏上垃圾桶，跨過石屎圍欄一躍而下，於是圍封現場，並追查兩人墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n  據悉，死亡男女為夫妻關係，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">結婚10多年，沒有兒女</span></span></strong>。男方叫「安仔」，為赤柱原居民，有7兄弟姊妹，他為孻仔，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">為人性格開朗</span></strong>，在赤柱賣紅酒，女方則為保安公司文員，兩人近期無異樣。男女雙方父母過身後，骨灰擺放於追遠堂不同樓層，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警方相信兩人拜祭父母後，雙雙墮樓輕生。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6fb3d81d6e0174fa6b902adac56df62735201854","tid":1711104,"uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:01:47.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191112/bkn-20191112141607472-1112_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191112%2Fbkn-20191112141607472-1112_00822_001.html&d=9CaroZtPfqcCLVRp0XVEkfsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=e9afb656\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191112/bkn-20191112141607472-1112_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ebde9d097603d5db5cfcd7a34f10fa3c57f01c50","tid":1711104,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:02:20.000Z","msg":"有冇人識佢地 知佢地有冇仔女"},{"pid":"03464a25fcb1678538eb11be416caf955863d29f","tid":17